20
00:05:02,636 --> 00:05:04,471
Jack, come on in.

21
00:05:07,641 --> 00:05:10,644
- How high is the pile on your desk?
- About this high.

22
00:05:10,644 --> 00:05:12,563
Now it's this high.

23
