At least to the lRS, who he feared
more than his own partners.

214
00:23:46,760 --> 00:23:50,222
According to the stockholder
statements he gave them, -

215
00:23:50,764 --> 00:23:53,767
- the shopping centres
weren't doing so well.

216
00:23:53,767 --> 00:23:57,771
But he was just skimming most of
the profits, 650 million dollars, -

217
00:23:58,772 --> 00:24:02,109
- and putting it in accounts
in Luxembourg, Panama -

218
00:24:02,734 --> 00:24:05,946
