03:16:04,682 --> 03:16:08,352
Not only can I expose you
to the press, so can the soldiers.

1423
03:16:09,687 --> 03:16:13,649
Do you want to take your chances
with the courts and the reporters?

1424
03:16:15,693 --> 03:16:19,196
To end the polit ical career
ofyour commander-in-chief?

1425
03:17:04,783 --> 03:17:06,285
Let's go!

1426
03:17:33,771 --> 03:17:36,857
Get your asses in here!
Come on, we got to go!

1427
03:17:40,820 --> 03:17:42,279
Come on!

1428
03:17:49,829 --> 03:17:51,831
Hold it! We wait for Ryan!

1429
03:17:51,831 --> 03:17:53,958
Yeah? We're out of here!

1430
03:18:01,799 --> 03:18:04,134
Set it down! He's down there!

1431
03:18:16,814 --> 03:18:18,274
Come on!

1432
03:18:37,877 --> 03:18:39,545
I've got you!

1433
03:18:45,843 --> 03:18:47,678
Chavez, cover me!

1434
03:18:57,855 --> 03:19:00,191
Your hand. Give me your hand!

1435
03:20:05,923 --> 03:20:08,342
The President wilI see you now.

1436
03:20:21,939 --> 03:20:24,191
Jack! I'm glad you're here.

1437
03:20:25,943 --> 03:20:28,529
Sit down.
Can I get you anything?

1438
03:20:29,989 --> 03:20:31,240
No.

1439
03:20:32,992 --> 03:20:36,328
- Come on, sit down.
- I would prefer to stand, sir.

1440
03:20:38,998 --> 03:20:42,751
Some things have gone on here
that I'm just becoming aware of.

1441
03:20:46,005 --> 03:20:49,550
I was kept in the dark, as you were,
for a very long time.

1442
03:20:49,967 --> 03:20:52,261
- Troubling things.
- Yeah.

1443
03:20:53,971 --> 03:20:57,975
Now we have to sort them out, figure
out who's responsible for what.

1444
03:20:57,975 --> 03:21:01,604
And what to do about it.
And we have to do it delicately, -

1445
03:21:01,979 --> 03:21:04,982
- otherwise people might
get the wrong idea.

1446
03:21:05,983 --> 03:21:07,735
We have to lie.

1447
03:21:09,028 --> 03:21:11,655
- Did I say that?
- No, you didn't.

1448
03:21:14,033 --> 03:21:16,368
- You're upset.
- I'm upset.

1449
03:21:18,037 --> 03:21:21,832
It's understandable. Do you mind
if I give you a bit of advice?

1450
03:21:24,043 --> 03:21:26,045
You know this, you're smart.

1451
03:21:26,045 --> 03:21:29,256
Never make important decisions
while you're upset.

1452
03:21:30,007 --> 03:21:33,844
You did. American soldiers and
civilians are dead because of it.

1453
03:21:36,013 --> 03:21:39,683
- I never ordered any...
- Don't you play that game with me!

1454
03:21:40,017 --> 03:21:43,896
Don't you dishonour their memories
by pretending you didn't know!

1455
03:21:44,021 --> 03:21:47,149
- How dare you lecture...
- How dare you, sir?!

1456
03:21:49,026 --> 03:21:52,655
How dare you come here
and bark at me like a junkyard dog!

1457
03:21:53,072 --> 03:21:55,908
I am the President
of the United States!

1458
03:21:59,078 --> 03:22:01,831
lt gives me no pleasure
to do it, sir.

1459
03:22:03,082 --> 03:22:06,627
As acting Deputy Director
of lntelligence it is my duty -

1460
03:22:07,086 --> 03:22:10,673
- to report this matter
to the Senate Oversight Committee.

1461
03:22:16,053 --> 03:22:18,931
- You're not going to do that.
- I'm not?

1462
03:22:24,061 --> 03:22:27,189
You've got yourself
a chip in the big game now.

1463
03:22:29,066 --> 03:22:33,195
You're going to save that for a time
when your own ass is on the line.

1464
03:22:34,113 --> 03:22:36,782
And then you're going to pull it out.

1465
03:22:38,117 --> 03:22:41,078
And I'm going to cash it in for you.
Right?

1466
03:22:45,124 --> 03:22:48,544
I don't think I have anything more
to say to you, sir.

1467
03:22:49,128 --> 03:22:53,090
The country can't afford another
scandal, Jack. To protect itseIf -

1468
03:22:55,092 --> 03:22:59,096
- it won't allow another deception
that goes all the way to the top.

1469
03:23:01,098 --> 03:23:04,852
You'll take the blame. Cutter
and Ritter will take some too, -

1470
03:23:05,102 --> 03:23:08,105
- but it will only amount to
a slap on the wrist.

1471
03:23:08,105 --> 03:23:11,400
Then 20,000 dollars an hour
on the lecture circuit.

1472
03:23:14,153 --> 03:23:17,031
The rest of the blame
will fall on Greer.

1473
03:23:18,157 --> 03:23:20,951
Oh yeah, you'll take him
down with you.

1474
03:23:22,161 --> 03:23:24,163
You'll destroy his reputation.

1475
03:23:24,163 --> 03:23:28,000
But that's as far as it will go.
The old Potomac two-step, Jack.

1476
03:23:33,172 --> 03:23:35,925
I'm sorry, Mr President,
I don't dance.

1477
03:24:00,199 --> 03:24:02,201
Ryan, have you got a minute?

1478
03:24:02,201 --> 03:24:03,452
No.

1479
03:24:05,204 --> 03:24:06,997
We need to talk!

1480
03:24:08,207 --> 03:24:09,542
Ryan!

1481
03:24:34,191 --> 03:24:38,028
The Committ ee will me to order.
The chair will w call Dr Ryan.

1482
03:25:01,218 --> 03:25:04,889
Dr Ryan, thank you for appearing
before the Committee today.

1483
03:25:07,224 --> 03:25:10,019
Please stand
and raise your right hand.

1484
03:25:14,231 --> 03:25:18,027
Do you solemnly swear that
the testimony you're about to give -

1485
03:25:19,278 --> 03:25:23,115
- is the whole truth and nothing
but the truth, so help you God?

1486
03:25:26,285 --> 03:25:27,620
I do.

1487
03:25:29,288 --> 03:25:33,125
Dr Ryan, you may consider yourself
under oath. Please be seated.

